-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/la/13-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/198014-%E3%80%8C%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8D%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E+%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條例有助官員釋除道歉對法律責任的顧慮</span></span></strong>，希望適時道歉，消除受影響人士的不滿情緖。<br />\n<br />\n  立法會議員涂謹申就指，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不排除有人以道歉去平息事件，用作逃避法律追究，甚至誇大道歉內容以博取信任，難以判斷是否真誠道歉</span></span></strong>，或會影響當事人是否追究的決定。他認為要小心平衡酌情權，以免<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道歉成為卸責手段</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共林鄭道歉只係鳩up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭用盡晒道歉法比佢既保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n林鄭幾識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88a45f5c86407afd27cccaf6730c88ce4c7275c","tid":1256701,"uid":268846,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"你以為係真心道歉就太天真喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n許志安個記者會又係真心道歉咩<br />\n形象工程嘅野你識條鐵<br />\n做一日半日演員有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5787b20dd34d0f9b3e34cc5a2bcd85668148ebe","tid":1256701,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"證明錯我會道歉希望人地諒解，如果唔係同班官同議員有咩分別"},{"pid":"deaa1007deb9c0bc268ba01a572a16d131b67e3b","tid":1256701,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">面對事實與付出代價，才是真道歉</span></strong><br />\n對比返林鄭無代價既道歉, 造成強烈對比"},{"pid":"f112080815d959914c2a79b387ed5c9e4ccae911","tid":1256701,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f